    <title>Arctic contributor: Véronique Morin</title>
    <description>Véronique Morin is an award winning science journalist and documentarian. She is currently working on a multi-platform documentary project on Indigenous Peoples and science. She was president of the Canadian Science Writers’ Association from 2001–2005 and the first president of the World Federation of Science Journalists from 2002–2004.
